Class DataTableIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataTableIO
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChemicalPropertiesTable
    public class DataTableIO
extends java.lang.Object
    Imports a comma-delimited txt file to read data and to add new data. The values in the table cannot be changed but new rows can be added, in which case the original file is also appended. Note: Exception is commented out
    Version:
    1.2 2017/10/31
